<br>
&quot;He will serve the God one way or another&quot; she concluded, and turned to the letter from Zippus. <br>
<br>
In the meanwhile she decided, she would go and observe Tanare for a while herself. The hints from the wizard, Zippus, were ....interesting.<br>
<br>
She also wondered at the stupid trolls, had they not yet replace the mirror. It was time to see to things more closely.<br>
