  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Um that don't make any sense- why do i need to be resuced and stuff? Or maybe this ranger knows a shortcut so i won't have to wait as long for my dress.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> Tanare thought to herself- the death threats and sacrifices that &quot;evil&quot; Dronkarr had spoken of already falling from her thoughts replaced by an obvious discomfort over the far too lenghty delay in getting her new dress. <br>
