  Realizing the ranger was probably waiting for a reply, Tanare frowned briefly as she saw her bow on the other side of the room out of reach. Her first plan to fire an arrow out with a message attached and hope it landed somewhere near the ranger had to be discarded. Looking around to make sure no one was near, she took a deep breathe and shouted &quot;OOOH YOU KNOW ANOTHER DRESS MAKING PLACE? wHEN DO THEY OPEN?&quot;<br>
